content:
The Wallboard in Omni Supervisor provides a snapshot of how agents are keeping up with their contact center workload. It shows key metrics for agents and work managed, based on selected queues or skills.

Available in: Salesforce Classic, Lightning Experience (not all orgs)

Focus the results by selecting specific queues or skills; 'AND' logic applies to multiple selections. Each metric displays the queues or skills used in filtering.

Choose from metric, donut, horizontal bar, or vertical bar chart display types for each chart.

Fields for the Omni Supervisor Wallboard tab include:

Sort and Filter in Omni Supervisor
Change Queues and Skills Assigned to Agents
Transfer a Work Item to a Different Skill Set
title: Service Cloud Wallboard Configuration
